column1: Shivin Narang is an Indian television actor known for portraying Ranvijay Singh in Ek Veer Ki Ardaas...Veera
column2: Jay Mittal in Internet Wala Love and for Rudra Roy in Sony TV's Beyhadh 2 opposite Jennifer Winget He was also a contestant of Fear Factor: Khatron Ke Khiladi 10 and was placed fifth.
